;
; Project Meridian — the NETWORKED world scene (issue #301). The real enter-world
; target: the root Node3D's script (world.gd) connects to the selected realm's
; worldd over the dedicated net thread and renders the local player + remote
; entities (a bot / another client) MOVING, so this scene file stays trivial.
; char_select.gd loads this on Enter World, passing the login session context via
; configure(session, character) before the scene enters the tree. The headless
; proof of the same net path is client/test/run_client_sees_bot_it.sh; the
; on-screen watch is scripts/dev/demo-networked.sh. camera_demo.tscn remains the
; standalone LOCAL demo.

[gd_scene load_steps=2 format=3 uid="uid://bwrld0net301aoi"]

[ext_resource type="Script" path="res://scenes/world/world.gd" id="1_world"]

[node name="World" type="Node3D"]
script = ExtResource("1_world")
